Sentencas: Sr0.15La0.85MnO3 layers with 2 and 10-mu-m thickness, deposited on zirconia based electrolytes, were evaluated as cathodes for high temperature applications.
Titulo: EVALUATION OF POROUS CERAMIC CATHODE LAYERS FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: Different electrode layers were characterized in terms of thickness, porosity, three phase boundary line per unit area (TPBL), and concentration polarization behavior.
Titulo: EVALUATION OF POROUS CERAMIC CATHODE LAYERS FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: Electrodes with maximum porosity and TPBL exhibit minimum concentration polarization losses at constant current density.
Titulo: EVALUATION OF POROUS CERAMIC CATHODE LAYERS FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
